            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@R.MartinhoFernandes how does one fix this &quot;broken&quot; problem?  The compiler can&apos;t tell if it&apos;s breaking or not.  This is only a concern when you are writing libraries for others, but you&apos;re making it out as universal zOMG here be dragons!&lt;/span&gt;

